text: For the first time in years, Kylie Jenner is not the queen of the Halloween scene. While most celebs are flocking to social media to flaunt their barely there ensembles and their festive imagination this weekend, Ky is taking some time to relax sans sexy costumes — in fact the celeb is covering up this Halloween season. Amid reports that the Keeping Up With the Kardashians star is pregnant with boyfriend Travis Scott ‘ s baby, the 20 - year - old has been laying low and not going out this holiday weekend. Today, the makeup mogul took to Snapchat and instead of posting party pics of herself wearing revealing costumes as she has done so in years past, she ’ s sharing Snapchats of herself in comfy clothes hanging out at home.
